rep_input: Clinically, what are the on-label points I should know about Trodelvy in HR+/HER2- after prior CDK4/6?
model_output: Trodelvy is indicated in HR-positive, HER2-negative advanced breast cancer after endocrine therapy and at least two prior systemic therapies, including a CDK4/6 inhibitor. The main on-label point is its use as a later-line option for patients who have progressed on standard treatments. For details on efficacy, tolerability, and patient selection, please send the EMA SmPC or EPAR by email.
